com.betterit.kaligia.service

Class MonitorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betterit.kaligia.service.MonitorService

  • @Service
public class MonitorService
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides asynchronous monitoring services for spectrometer.

    Spectrometer parameter values are appended with a String "XX" so that they can be retrieved using the same emmitter at the calibrationdashboard.js file This string is used to differentiate the parameters
